{"tid":2402127,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中紀錄片《Do Not Split 不割席》 入圍奧斯卡最佳紀錄短片（10強）","createTime":"2021-02-10T08:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T08:24:54.000Z","uid":41343,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b74efa8d5d201ea1f693ce026e7a1b509bfb68","tid":2402127,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"由挪威導演Anders Hammer執導，以反送中為題材的紀錄片《Do Not Split 不割席》，有份入圍奧斯卡最佳紀錄短片，導演於Twitter上宣佈喜訊。<br />\n<br />\n導演表示：「我們關於香港示威的紀錄片《Do Not Split 不割席》，成為了奧斯卡最佳紀錄短片10套入圍作品其中一套。」《Do Not Split 不割席》是一部30分鐘的紀錄片，講述香港的抗爭並非虛張聲勢，而是一場場的實戰，以對抗持有武器的警察。片中紀錄了抗爭者的決心與犧牲，而政府卻未有退讓，更通過了北京支持的國安法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210210/A2PEWIT3HJA3LC4XL6UZYACRBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210210%2FA2PEWIT3HJA3LC4XL6UZYACRBE%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhbKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=ff6a7c76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210210%2FA2PEWIT3HJA3LC4XL6UZYACRBE%2F&h=4b156255\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210210/A2PEWIT3HJA3LC4XL6UZYACRBE/</a>"},{"pid":"a0889c300636c2fcd1c2379099e53b574f722239","tid":2402127,"uid":132302,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"Youtube 有得免費睇全片支持下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BpS-Y7ndNeQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBpS-Y7ndNeQ&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhbKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=a3ba48dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BpS-Y7ndNeQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://fieldofvision.org/do-not-split\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffieldofvision.org%2Fdo-not-split&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhbKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=0f1857f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fieldofvision.org/do-not-split</a>"},{"pid":"cf